'''佩蒂翁维尔学校倒塌事故'''发生于2008年11月7日，一间位于[[海地|海地]]首都[[太子港|太子港]]郊区[[佩蒂翁维尔|佩蒂翁维尔]]（{{lang|en|Pétionville}}）的名为“诺言学院”（The Evangelic Promise）的教会学校的教学大楼在当地时间早上10:00左右突然倒塌。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2008-11/09/content_10329992.htm |title=news.xinhuanet.com, Death toll in Haitian school collapse rises to 92 |access-date=2008-11-10 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304023811/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2008-11/09/content_10329992.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="AFP">{{cite news|url=http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5h_imjKUfz61aWKiTjo3DgsF6gskA|title=50 dead in Haitian grade-school collapse|date=2008-11-08|publisher=AFP|accessdate=2008-11-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110520185713/http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5h_imjKUfz61aWKiTjo3DgsF6gskA|archivedate=2011-05-20}}</ref>事故导致超过500名学生和多名教师活埋在瓦砾之下；至今已造成至少93死150伤，估计死亡人数会持续上升。<ref name="AP">{{cite news|url=http://ap.google.com/article/ALeqM5hHOomf3U8hUR7ep44gyz4xKgtuOQD94AE87G0|title=Death toll in Haiti school collapse rises to 30|last=Katz|first=Jonathan M.|date=2008-11-07|publisher=AP|accessdate=2008-11-08}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name="SundayTimes93">{{cite news|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/us_and_americas/article5119867.ece|title=Classroom of corpses dug from rubble after Haiti school collapse|publisher=The Sunday Times|accessdate=2008-11-10}}</ref><ref name="Guardian">{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2008/nov/09/haiti-school-collapse-disaster|title=Haiti school collapse: 200 feared missing|publisher=The Observer|accessdate=2008-11-09|archive-date=2012-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114033945/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2008/nov/09/haiti-school-collapse-disaster|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==倒塌==
教学大楼的一楼被二楼和三楼紧紧压在下面，教学楼的倒塌还压倒了附近的几所民居。<ref name="BBC">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/7716516.stm|title=Deadly school collapse in Haiti|date=2008-11-08|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2008-11-08|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410230713/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/7716516.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AP84">{{cite news|url=http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5hgnHaEEMVynAbrKsBGQUkNpb4EAw|title=84 killed, 150 injured in Haitian school collapse|date=2008-11-09|publisher=Associated Press|accessdate=2008-11-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110520185747/http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5hgnHaEEMVynAbrKsBGQUkNpb4EAw|archivedate=2011-05-20}}</ref><ref name="BBC"/>而学生主要分布在一楼和二楼，也有部分学生当时在操场上。<ref name="CNN">{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/americas/11/07/haiti.school.collapse/|title=Rescue continues into the night after Haiti school collapses|date=2008-11-08|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2008-11-08|archive-date=2021-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314164323/http://edition.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/americas/11/07/haiti.school.collapse/|dead-url=no}}</ref>倒塌的原因尚未正式公布，但是[[海地总统|海地总统]][[勒内·普雷瓦尔|勒内·普雷瓦尔]]8日视察完现场后表示，学校为[[混凝土|混凝土]]构造，建筑质量低劣，没有使用任何[[钢筋|钢筋]]，以及有关部门监督不力为倒塌的主要原因。<ref name="BBC"/>这所学校在2000年也曾经试过一次小规模的倒塌，后来重建了。<ref name="AP"/>而此次倒塌的时候，教学楼的三楼还正在建造。<ref name="katz">{{cite news |last=Katz |first=Jonathan |date=2008-11-07 |publisher=Associated Press |title=Death toll in Haiti school collapse rises to 30 |url=http://ap.google.com/article/ALeqM5hHOomf3U8hUR7ep44gyz4xKgtuOQD94ABHMO0 |accessdate=2008-11-07 }}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

==责任==
学校的负责人福尔廷·奥古斯廷牧师承认，这所学校全部由他设计建造，建造期间没有雇用任何建筑工程师。他于11月8日被捕，被控[[过失杀人|过失杀人]]。<ref>[http://canadianpress.google.com/article/ALeqM5i3jsMrv2mc_brMsaULSfRJLfmk-Q  canadianpress.google.com, Owner of collapsed Haiti school arrested] {{webarchive|url=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20110520000000/http://canadianpress.google.com/article/ALeqM5i3jsMrv2mc_brMsaULSfRJLfmk-Q |date=2011-05-20 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.macaunews.net/story/427823 |title=macaunews.net, Haiti school owner in custody |accessdate=2008-11-10 |archive-date=2009-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090104143040/http://www.macaunews.net/story/427823 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==救援==
多个国家和组织都对此次事故表示关切和哀悼。海地的邻国[[多米尼加共和国|多米尼加共和国]]、[[法国|法国]]的[[马提尼克|马提尼克]]、[[无国界医生|无国界医生]]、联合国驻海地维和部队、[[红十字会|红十字会]]、[[美国国际开发署|美国国际开发署]]等都派救援队伍前往协助救援。<ref name="katz"/><ref>{{cite news|first=|last=|coauthors=|title=50 dead in Haitian grade-school collapse|work=Agence France-Presse|page=|date=2008-11-08|accessdate=2008-11-08|quote=|url=http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5h_imjKUfz61aWKiTjo3DgsF6gskA|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110520185713/http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5h_imjKUfz61aWKiTjo3DgsF6gskA|archivedate=2011-05-20}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.marketwatch.com/news/story/USAID-Responds-Immediately-Haitian-School/story.aspx?guid=%7B997A3A3F-014B-4796-8834-E3BD6DD65D91%7D|title=USAID Responds Immediately to Haitian School Collapse|date=2008-11-07|publisher=Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2008-11-08}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2008-11/09/content_10329992.htm |title=news.xinhuanet.com, Death toll in Haitian school collapse rises to 92  |access-date=2008-11-10 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304023811/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2008-11/09/content_10329992.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

